<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Support</h1>

  <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get Help</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We're here to help you get the most out of PocketLedger.
        Whether you have questions, need technical assistance, or want to provide feedback, we'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Methods</h2>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Email Support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
          For general inquiries, technical support, or bug reports:
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          <%= link_to "support@pocketledger.com", "mailto:support@pocketledger.com", class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium" %>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">We typically respond within 24-48 hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Feature Requests & Feedback</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
          Have an idea for a new feature or improvement?
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          <%= link_to "feedback@pocketledger.com", "mailto:feedback@pocketledger.com", class: "text-green-600 hover:text-green-800 font-medium" %>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">We love hearing from our users!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Account & Billing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
          Questions about subscriptions, payments, or account issues?
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          <%= link_to "billing@pocketledger.com", "mailto:billing@pocketledger.com", class: "text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-800 font-medium" %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How do I attach receipts to expenses?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            When creating or editing an expense, use the "Receipt/Invoice Files" field to upload images (JPG, PNG) or PDF files.
            You can attach multiple files to a single expense.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I set up recurring expenses?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Yes! When creating an expense, check the "Make this a recurring expense" box.
            You can set the frequency (daily, weekly, monthly, yearly) and specify start/end dates.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How do I export my expense data?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            You can export your expenses to CSV or PDF format from the expenses page.
            This is useful for sharing with accountants or filing taxes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is my data secure?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Yes. We use industry-standard encryption for data transmission (HTTPS/SSL) and storage.
            Your password is encrypted using bcrypt. See our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %> for details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I delete my account and data?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Yes. You can delete your account at any time through your account settings.
            All your expense records and uploaded files will be permanently deleted within 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What file formats are supported for receipts?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We support common image formats (JPG, PNG, GIF) and PDF files. Each file should be under 10MB.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer a mobile app?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Currently, PocketLedger is a web application optimized for mobile browsers.
            A dedicated mobile app is planned for the future.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Report a Bug</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Found a bug? Please email us at <%= link_to "support@pocketledger.com", "mailto:support@pocketledger.com", class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %> with:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>A description of the problem</li>
        <li>Steps to reproduce the issue</li>
        <li>Your browser and operating system</li>
        <li>Screenshots if applicable</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Additional Resources</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li><%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %> - How we protect your data</li>
        <li><%= link_to "Terms of Service", terms_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %> - Usage terms and conditions</li>
        <li><%= link_to "About PocketLedger", about_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %> - Learn more about our mission</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 text-center">
    <%= link_to "â† Back to Home", root_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800" %>
  </div>
</div>
